== Others == {{Expand list|date=November 2010}}
Note that the major regions, such as [[Africa]] and [[Eurasia]], are sorted alphabetically, whereas the minor regions, such as Northeast and Northwest Africa in [[#Africa|Africa]], and Arabia and South Asia in [[#Eurasia|Eurasia]], are sorted by the dates in which their first mosques were reportedly established, more or less, barring those that are [[#Named in the Quran|mentioned by name in the Quran]].
