=== Eurasia === {{See also|List of mosques in Asia|List of mosques in Europe}}
'[[Eurasia]]' is treated here not as a continental landmass, but a combination of [[Europe]]an and [[Asia]]n countries, including [[island]]-states such as Japan and the United Kingdom.
