{{Expand Serbian|Vojislav Korać|date=December 2014}}
'''Vojislav Korać''' (1924–2010) was a Yugoslav and Serbian historian on architecture, academic and professor. An ethnic Serb, he was born in [[Debelo Brdo]] in [[Udbina]], [[Kingdom of Yugoslavia]] (now [[Croatia]]).

